.modal-wrapper.bulma
    .modal#settings-modal
        .modal-background
        .modal-card
            header.modal-card-head
                p.modal-card-title CGS Schedule Settings
            section.modal-card-body
                .field
                    label.label
                        | Theme
                        i.fas.fa-palette.p-l-sm
                    .field.has-addons
                        .control.is-expanded
                            .select.is-fullwidth
                                select#theme
                        .control
                            a.button( target = '_blank' href='https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1kfA4DS8-bV-ngZYRQwt4hAqMVSQDeGjU71BqfnR9MlY/edit#gid=1757467265' ) Create New Theme
                    p.help Selects a user-created color theme for the schedule.
                .field
                    label.label
                        | Class Homepage Links
                        i.fas.fa-link.p-l-sm
                    .control
                        input#class-links.switch.is-rounded.is-medium.is-info(type='checkbox' name='class-links' checked='checked')
                        label(for='class-links')
                        a.button( target = '_blank' href='https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1kfA4DS8-bV-ngZYRQwt4hAqMVSQDeGjU71BqfnR9MlY/edit#gid=0' ) Add More Links
                    p.help
                        | Enables or disables user-added class links. Useful for homework calendars.
                .field
                    label.label
                        | Canvas Calendar Events
                        i.far.fa-calendar-alt.p-l-sm
                    .control
                        input#calendar-events.switch.is-rounded.is-success(type='checkbox' name='calendar-events' checked='checked')
                        label(for='calendar-events')
                    p.help
                        | Enables or disables inline canvas calendar events.
                        | #[a( target = '_blank' href='https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1kfA4DS8-bV-ngZYRQwt4hAqMVSQDeGjU71BqfnR9MlY/edit#gid=1673690997' ) Add more calendars.]
                .field
                    label.label
                        | Next Day Highlighting
                        i.fas.fa-highlighter.p-l-sm
                    .control
                        input#day-highlight.switch.is-rounded.is-medium(type='checkbox' name='day-highlight' checked='checked')
                        label(for='day-highlight')
                    p.help
                        | Enables or disables highlighting of the current day in week view.
                .field
                    label.label
                        | Tips
                        i.fas.fa-lightbulb.p-l-sm
                    p.help
                        | - #[a( target = '_blank' href='https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1kfA4DS8-bV-ngZYRQwt4hAqMVSQDeGjU71BqfnR9MlY/edit#gid=0' ) Add links]
                        | to the homework calendar for each of your classes
                        br
                        | - Left-click on class blocks to open the first link for your class
                        br
                        | - Hold the "ctrl" or "command" key and left click on multiple blocks to open several new links
                        br
                        | - Right-click on class blocks to see a list of all the links for your class
                        br
                        | - Click on any date label (Mon Oct 14) to view the day's schedule in Veracross
                        br
                        | - On touchscreen devices, swipe left and right to navigate between days
                        br
                        | - The schedule is mobile-friendly, just click on the "Today" view and text the link to your phone

            footer.modal-card-foot
                button.button.is-info#save-settings Save changes
                button.button#cancel-settings Cancel
                div(style="text-align: right; width: 100%")
                    a(target="_blank" href="https://github.com/CGScheduleSquad/cgs-schedule")
                        | CGS Schedule is open-source on GitHub
